<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Support Ticket Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .ticket-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .ticket-message {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .priority-high {
      color: #d9534f;
    }
    .priority-medium {
      color: #f0ad4e;
    }
    .priority-low {
      color: #5cb85c;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Support Ticket Created</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for contacting AutoHub support. Your support ticket has been created successfully and is now being processed by our team.</p>
    
    <div class="ticket-details">
      <h2>Ticket Details</h2>
      <p><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> {{ticketId}}</p>
      <p><strong>Subject:</strong> {{subject}}</p>
      <p><strong>Priority:</strong> 
        {{#if (eq priority "high")}}
        <span class="priority-high">High</span>
        {{else if (eq priority "medium")}}
        <span class="priority-medium">Medium</span>
        {{else}}
        <span class="priority-low">Low</span>
        {{/if}}
      </p>
      
      <h3>Your Message:</h3>
      <div class="ticket-message">
        <p>{{message}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p>Our support team will review your ticket and respond as soon as possible. You can check the status of your ticket or add additional information by clicking the button below:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="#" class="button">View Ticket Status</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>We aim to respond to all tickets within 24-48 hours, depending on the priority and complexity of the issue.</p>
    <p>Thank you for your patience and for choosing AutoHub.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The AutoHub Support Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 AutoHub. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>Please do not reply directly to this email. To add more information to your ticket, please use the link above.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>